When you put on these headphones, you can hear the effects of the atoms emitted by the radioactivity of the minerals".
Evans: "Say, it's definitely going to pop now!"
"Hans" Geiger died in 1945, just a few days after his 63rd birthday.
But the invention that bears his name survives.
